OL,3,CUK inflation rate falls to 2.8%
OL,4,Cdespite rising cost of fuel
OL,6,FThe UK's annual inflation rate fell to
OL,7,F2.8% in April, the Office for National
OL,8,FStatistics said on Wednesday.
OL,10,FExperts had expected the the rate to
OL,11,Fdecrease from 3.3% in March, to around
OL,12,F3% as household energy bills dropped
OL,13,Fto offset a jump in fuel prices last
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FOfgem lowered its energy price cap
OL,17,Ffrom the start of April by 7%, or #10
OL,18,Fa month, for the average household
OL,19,Fusing both electricity and gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
