OL,3,CUK inflation rate falls to 2.8%
OL,4,Cdespite rising cost of fuel
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe new figure means that prices are
OL,12,Fstill rising year-on-year, but at a
OL,13,Fslower rate than they were the month
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,F"There was a notable fall in annual
OL,17,Finflation led by lower electricity and
OL,18,Fgas prices," said ONS Chief Economist
OL,19,FGrant Fitzner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
