OL,3,CUK inflation rate falls to 2.8%
OL,4,Cdespite rising cost of fuel
OL,6,F"This was due to the government's
OL,7,Fenergy bill support package reducing
OL,8,Fvariable and fixed tariffs, along with
OL,9,Flower global wholesale energy prices
OL,10,Fbefore the conflict in the Middle
OL,11,FEast, which fed through to the
OL,12,Freduction in the Ofgem cap.
OL,14,F"Smaller rises in water and sewage
OL,15,Fbills and Vehicle Excise Duty than
OL,16,Fseen last year also helped pull the
OL,17,Frate down. Food prices, particularly
OL,18,Ffor chocolate and meat products, and
OL,19,Fthe price of package holidays drove
OL,20,Finflation down further.
