OL,3,CUK inflation rate falls to 2.8%
OL,4,Cdespite rising cost of fuel
OL,6,F"These were only partially offset by a
OL,7,Ffurther increase in petrol and diesel
OL,8,Fprices, and an uptick in the cost of
OL,9,Fclothing and footwear.
OL,11,F"The annual cost of both raw materials
OL,12,Fand goods leaving factories continued
OL,13,Fto rise, driven again by higher crude
OL,14,Foil and petrol prices."
